name: Illuminations Nocturnes
description:
May 2019, my first night in Japan.

Walking around Kawanishi Ikeda near my accommodation with my camera, this was the beginning of my 3 months trip in Japan, an iconic view for me in front of the train station. I was immediately captivated by the neon illuminations.

Such a colorful and spectacular show.

[24x36 inch print for collector]
